<currency>:[<crap>][<role>][<action>]<term>|[<crap>][<action>]<term>[<role>]|[<crap>][<role>][<action>]<term>[<value>][<unit>]|[<role>][<crap>][<action>]<term>|[<role>][<injectionAct>][<term>];
<injection>:[<crap>][<role>]<injectionAct><drugs><value>[<unit>]|[<crap>][<role>]<drugs><value>[<unit>]<injectionAct>|[<crap>][<role>]<value>[<unit>]<drugs><injectionAct>;
<prepare>:[<crap>][<role>]<action><drugs>[<value>][<unit>]|[<crap>]<action><drugs>[<value>][<unit>][<role>]|[<crap>][<role>]<action>[<value>][<unit>]<drugs>;